thread.title: BRIEF-Kernel Holding Q2 2017/2018 Net Profit Down At $67 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Kernel Holding Q2 2017/2018 Net Profit Down At $67 Mln
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - KERNEL HOLDING SA:
* Q2 2017/2018 NET PROFIT USD 67.0 MILLION VERSUS USD 95.4 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q2 2017/2018 REVENUE USD 536.1 MILLION VERSUS USD 659.3 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q2 2017/2018 EBITDA USD 77.1 MILLION VERSUS USD 129.8 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q2 2017/2018 OPERATING PROFIT USD 55.9 MILLION VERSUS USD 116.1 MILLION YEAR AGO
